fifthMain.name: Gravity Crush
fifthMain.shortDesc:
MP Cost: 1000, Draw in up to 8 enemies in range, stunning them, and create a singularity which periodically deals 1500% damage. Number of attacks: 3.
Singularity Duration: 30 sec. When the skill duration ends, the singularity explodes dealing 2400% AoE damage over a large range.
The damage of the AoE attack can increase up to 6000% based on the damage inflicted by the caster or a party member while the enemy is within the Singularity.
Cooldown: 120 sec
fifthMain.desc: Creates a vortex that pulls in and damages nearby enemies
details:
At the end of the Skill, the vortex will explode dealing massive damage
  • Based on how much damage was dealt to enemies inside the vortex, the explosion will deal increased damage

fifthMain.name: Suborbital Strike
fifthMain.shortDesc:
MP Cost: 1000, Summons drones for 90 sec. The drones have two modes of operation, and you can switch between them every 3 sec. Drone attacks prioritize the enemy with the highest Max HP within range.
[Beam Splitter] The drones hover above 4 targets within range, and fire downward periodically dealing 450% damage to up to 8 enemies 4 times.
[Beam Amplifier] Drone hovers over 1 target within range and blasts downward periodically dealing 365% damage to up to 10 enemies 10 times.
Cooldown: 180 sec
fifthMain.desc: Summons drones above your character that damages nearby enemies
details: The drones will seek out enemies with the highest max HP

fifthMain.name: Allied Fury
fifthMain.shortDesc:
MP Cost: 60, summons fellow bounty hunters to attack enemies and mark any enemies that are not defeated, Max Enemies Hit: 15, Damage: 500, Number of Attacks: 10.
Attacks marked enemies with an airship for 600% damage 8 times.
Focused Attack: If attacking a single target, the total number of attacks increase by 4.
Cooldown: 6 sec
fifthMain.desc: Bounty hunters appear to help take down enemies before an airship comes to deliver a final attack
details: If attacking a single enemy, attack deals increased number of hits per attack
